/>\n<br />\n習姓也在白頭翁裡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"又解得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"最後兩句詩好得人驚<br />\n<br />\n東邊是台灣-<br />\n南海是後門<br />\n美國增加 在台灣海軍活動和在南海附近發射導彈<br />\n<br />\n希望我的解釋是錯誤的"},{"pid":"d7e858db1c83788e962df0451af59abe8b71bdc7","tid":1940294,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/af/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80%E4%B8%83%E7%A8%AE.pdf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Faf%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25B8%2583%25E7%25A8%25AE.pdf&h=a0749831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我daddy借 我帳戶一用<br />\n<br />\n推背圖 <br />\n預言中國的命運<br />\n總共六十象<br />\n從唐朝開始<br />\n解釋的人是清初的和尚(?)<br />\n他解釋至第三十三象<br />\n我daddy 解釋 34至41象，但不太確定42至46象"},{"pid":"f0cb3ad0d7cf5baafc7958a2f59b05c51bd1d3d7","tid":1940294,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T17:32:00.000Z","msg":"解釋的人是清初的金聖嘆<br />\n他解釋至第三十三象<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金聖嘆（1608年4月17日－1661年8月7日），本名金人瑞，又名金采，字聖歎，蘇州人，明末清初著名文學批評家，被推崇為中國白話文運動的先驅，在中國文學史上佔有重要地位。"},{"pid":"1029ebaf3409545040fe7dd358b076789d6465c2","tid":1940294,"uid":276987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7e858db1c83788e962df0451af59abe8b71bdc7","tid":1940294,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/af/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80%E4%B8%83%E7%A8%AE.pdf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Faf%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25B8%2583%25E7%25A8%25AE.pdf&h=a0749831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我daddy借 我帳戶一用<br />\n<br />\n推