ps://youtu.be/s29R3D422m4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs29R3D422m4&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1iZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=54f61013\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s29R3D422m4</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG Web 分享一則貼文：【時事台】推背圖第四十五象與武漢肺炎<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7196835/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7196835%2Fpage%2F1&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1iZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=409026df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7196835/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"以後無奧運？唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d577141b2f96868459c67d32e1d9636d1cd4a3fc","tid":1940294,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f94c819a9c2507a21530e0325f0ca0f030a2c9","tid":1940294,"uid":276987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T01:35:13.000Z","msg":"34象<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXFJQNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXFJQNU.jpg&h=6a87f021&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T20:05:16.000Z","msg":"太平天國<br />\n所有北，南，東，西王互相殘殺<br />\n洪秀全  名字在這首詩的最後一句<br />\n第一個字    洪<br />\n第七字        秀<br />\n第十三字     全<br />\n<br />\n頭有髮- 長毛賊  - 不像清朝人那樣剃光頭<br />\n因清朝推行薙髮令，太平天國蓄髮、披髮，故太平軍被稱作「長毛」，清廷稱其為「長毛賊」、「毛賊」、「髮賊」、「髮匪」、「髮逆」等<br />\n<br />\n衣怕白- 拜上帝會起家- 可能穿著白色的長袍<br />\n<br />\nmake sense?"},{"pid":"f790cf83b51c3102b1b77ad58b3a64b08a7ff4a0","tid":1940294,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17d0361630a10dc1c091aac8f94e239b724c5c57","tid":1940294,"uid":276987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T01:35:44.000Z","msg":"35象<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dS7zXtb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdS7zXtb.jpg&h=9df1c90a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T20:16:51.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍是指1900年（清光緒二十六年）為了鎮壓義和團運動及擴大在華特權，以軍事行動攻入大清的英國、美國、法國、德國、俄羅斯、日本、奧匈帝國、義大利的八國聯合軍隊<br />\n<br />\n八國聯軍直接造成義和團被消滅，以及京津一帶清軍的潰敗，迫使慈禧太后挾光緒帝逃往陝西西安；最終清廷與包含派兵八國在內的十一國簽訂不平等的《辛丑和約》，付出龐大的賠款，並條約允許各國在北京駐軍及構築永久要塞。<br />\n<br />\n西方有人......八國聯軍攻入大清<br />\n帝出不還.....光緒帝逃往陝西西安<br />\n 三台....       派載勛任步軍統領，會剛毅、載漪、載濂、載瀾等親貴統領義和團 - just guessing this one"},{"pid":"1b806d730d08c11c5e6739c8cd5bdc0c33e0baf0","tid":1940294,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6152daf41c52db7f310d94e519a01d8fe8216d9e","tid":1940294,"uid":276987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T01:36:23.000Z","msg":"36象<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dpXL38p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdpXL38p.jpg&h=2663a5d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T20:26:11.000Z","msg":"慈禧太后-垂簾聽政-.發動戊戌政變-獨掌大權<br />\n清朝的病鵝"},{"pid":"3026be30993c6137ab38426ab02d80de054355d0","tid":1940294,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6add1dd1e02b0b5cfee3ecd4b298b625850cea7f","tid":1940294,"uid":276987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T01:37:23.000Z","msg":"37象<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/077TtAp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F077TtAp.jpg&h=b6afc900&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T20:54:18.000Z","msg":"圖片<br />\n黎人-少數民族名,住在海南島- 黎<br />\n抱著頭-元首                             元<br />\n在洪水中                                  洪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民國四年（1915年），袁世凱復辟帝制，冊封黎元洪為&ldquo;武義親王&rdquo;，黎元洪堅辭不就。民國五年（1916年）6月，袁世凱死後，黎元洪繼任大總統，<br />\n袁世凱想要 復辟帝制.黎元洪真的是不想復辟的總統.<br />\n不統繼統.海內竟無王-  中國已經結束王朝 制度<br />\n統治者不由繼承的, 是選舉產生的<br />\n<br />\n倒 gor Fung 八月-1911年10月10日是 農曆八月十九<br />\n武昌起義是1911年10月10日（清&middot;宣統三年八月十九）"},{"pid":"3df6982ae8c379a9f4de2aed8a4e694812acda64","tid":1940294,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5277c554e8d7b8c83170e2f08807b90818120abd","tid":1940294,"uid":276987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"38象<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJ6QvOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJ6QvOU.jpg&h=353477a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T20:58:43.000Z","msg":"軍閥割據時期<br />\n<br />\n參見：軍閥之間戰鬥列表<br />\n袁世凱逝後無人有聲望和能力統御整個北洋軍，北洋軍遂分裂為直系、皖系、奉系等三大割據勢力，統稱北洋軍閥。而在護國戰爭後，各地軍閥亦成形，如桂系、滇系、粵系、川軍&hellip;&hellip;等。各地軍閥在名義上仍受北京的中央政府支配，但實際上各自為政，有如獨立王國。從1916年6月至1919年五四運動爆發，中央政府實際為皖系軍閥所控制，後來分別為直系、皖系、奉系軍閥輪流掌握。<br />\n<br />\n總結來說-一團糟"}]}